volume.name: Santa's Favorite Tales: Holiday Comics for Grown-Up Kids

description: Raven and Cyborg create a pair of spooky-looking leggings from a pattern in one of Ravens arcane books. But Robins in for quite the fright when he tries on these Scaredy Pants!
name: Scaredy Pants

description: A red-hot collectible previously only available at the Sundance Film Festival, Smodcomics proudly presents the official prequel to Kevin Smith's Yoga Hosers, starring Johnny Depp, Harley Quinn Smith, and Lily-Rose Depp! Since the remarkably charismatic duo of Colleen C. and Colleen M. debuted in the horror-comedy film Tusk, fans have been clamoring for more of these 15-year-old yoga nuts... and with Yoga Hosers: A Sundance Super Special, True North Trilogy devotees will finally see the continuation of their story! What is the secret eh-rigin of these convenience store clerks destined to face the monsters of Manitoba? How did fate bring two Colleens together to survive all the craziness that Winnipeg could throw at them? And can they harness Moksha, the ultimate goal of yoga, to destroy everything that threatens the things they love, eh?

volume.name: Yoga Hosers: A Sundance Super Special!

description:
A Devastation Among Us!

Max is in the infirmary after the events of Issue #1. Now it is time for the remaining members, Faceless and Krimson, to pick up the pieces. Their trail leads them to Russia to confront the ex boxer, The Devastator. In the meantime, Dr. Specter gathers his terrorist group Axiom to attack a defenseless Station Zero!
name: A Devastation Among Us!

description: Two worlds collide on a distant planet. Revolving around its star but failing to rotate has created two extremes - a side of eternal sunlight and one of maddening darkness. At the border where light fades into dark, one man controls it all. Fueled by revenge, hatred and love, three friends set out to stop the corruption and start their world spinning, changing their lives forever.
name: Part 2

description:
Our naughty little WitchGirl is back at last in her own magazine, with two brand-new stories by Dennis Mallonee and Gordon Purcell!

First, enjoy a blast from the past! When the Black Enchantress gets her hands on the gemstones of Dark Malice, it's her turn to deal with those annoying Greek gods during "Andrea's Adventure in Olympus."

Then get ready to meet Doctor Arcane's newest girlfriend, the demonic WitchGirl DANIELLE. In her civilian identity, she's a high-priced lawyer, but she's also a genuine princess of Hell!

Green Web

Five years ago a serial killer emerged in California, murdering women and staging them in a very specific manner. He signed his crimes with a smiley face drawn with the blood of his victims. The press dubbed him Red Smile. Brian Warner, the lead investigator in the case, spent the last five years hunting him. In retaliation, Red Smile killed Brian's family before Brian got home. Brian went after the killer and found that Red Smile has a fan club of people who kill to impress their idol. Now Brian has to take things to the next level...
name: Green Web

description:
After a fateful encounter with a trio of vengeful highwaymen, Bremen learns of a sizable bounty placed on his head from none other than Luyin, the beautiful yet sinister agent of Lord Jacque Bontemps.

Bremen's situation becomes far more perilous and the stakes much higher as he ponders what options he has left.

Mikhail the Meat Man

If Kurtis Kasey: The Body Snatcher wasn't enough already, our Chaos Trio face a new slasher: Mikhail the Meat Man!

Note: This issue takes place between Chaos Campus #6 and 7.
name: Mikhail the Meat Man

description: Ghost is trapped in Chicago, and the noose continues to tighten around his neck as the Dead Mans Party rages on. Even as he fights to stay alive, Ghost makes a shocking discovery that will upend his life. Or death.

The town of Bonesnap has seen its fair share of reckless gunslingers. But when an idealistic white-haired young demon comes to town, all hell threatens to break loose. This ain't your typical wild west tale.
Guardian Corgi and her quirky, talking "animal" companion are back for another adventure! Some local dogs have turned up brainwashed-- who could be behind this evil deed?

Wine and Vines part 2 of 3

The spirit world looks to be under attack in the latest installment of hillbilly horror hoedown. Buy this comic, Dummy!

Roots run deep in the south.
name: Wine and Vines Part 2 of 3

description: Henry is a simple hamster living among the drunken mice of Hooch Springs. When the evil rat empire shows up at his doorstep, intending to enslave him, Henry might have to become the ruthless killing machine he was destined to be.

Some people will do anything to make it in the music industry. Some have even considered selling their souls.

What if your soul was the only thing you had left and to save it, you had to take out the evil in the industry you grew up dreaming to one day be a part of?

This is what life on tour with Jezibelle is all about...

The Fall

Agent attempts to rally support and save Armani before it's to late.
name: The Fall

Fun with stock photography!

Journey into the seventh issue of Nobody Can Eat 50 Eggs with articles such as: Preventing the Ape-Pocalypse, The Fish With Mind Powers, A Brief Interview with Randolph Pizza AND MORE!
name: Fun With Stock Photography!

description: Richard meets his maker, but there's more to him than meets the eye.
